HEADWORD: Enhancement
<hw>En*hance"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of
increasing, or state of being increased; augmentation; aggravation;
<as>as, the <ex>enhancement</ex> of value, price, enjoyments,
crime</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

